codex
The core replay code is visible now: it does compute a slide vector after the contact, but only 
appends final waypoints when a later `findFirstContact` reports no contact. I’m checking how 
`FloorMesh::pathWalkCircle` packages the hit into `FloorLocator`, especially contact time and normal.
